Orascom Construction Upgraded to ‘Buy’ From ‘Neutral’ at EFG

-- B y   A l a a   S h a h i n e
-- 
2011-09-27T19:15:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/orascom-construction-upgraded-to-buy-from-neutral-at-efg.html
Orascom Construction Industries was
upgraded to “buy” from “neutral” at EFG-Hermes Holding SAE,
which said the sell-off of  Egypt ’s biggest publicly-traded
builder was “overdone.”  Orascom’s share-price estimate was maintained at 265
Egyptian pounds, EFG said in an e-mailed report. Orascom’s
shares tumbled 4.2 percent to 218.94 pounds at the 2:30 p.m.
close in Cairo.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alaa Shahine in New York at 
